These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, azalea, amaryllis
There 4 different types of food: mango, lemon, grapes, lettuce
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, turquise, green
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, volleyball, tennis, badminton
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, domino, whist
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bongani, prince, swisher
 1. the person playing whist is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person eating mango is the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
 8. the game-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person eating grapes is the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the game-smoker is the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
12. the person eating lettuce is the person who growsiris##1
13. the person eating mango is in an even position##4
14. the person eating lettuce is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
15. the person who likes lavender is the person who growsiris##1
16. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
17. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4        |
| Flower         | amaryllis    | bellflower      | azalea | iris        |
| Food           | grapes | mango     | lemon     | lettuce |
| Color   | fuchsia   | turquise | green   | lavender         |
| Sport   | ice-hockey  | badminton        | tennis   | volleyball            |
| Game           | chess       | bridge  | whist    | domino         |
| Cigar     | game       | bongani     | swisher     | prince      |

