There are 4 different nationalities: indian, canadian, thai, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, snowboarding, biathlon
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, videographer, mechanic, firefighter
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, lily, daisy, azalea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, september, july, october
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 2. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the mechanic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the indian is the firefighter##1
 5. the indian is the person who growslily##1
 6. the videographer is the canadian##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the canadian is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's birthday is in october##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who growsazalea is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
15. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
16. the japanese is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
17. the mechanic is on the left or right of the japanese##3
18. the mechanic is on the right of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
