 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 4. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsrose is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the trike##1
 7. the fan of d&b is between the fan of jazz and the person who growsmarigold##2
 8. the person traveling to colone is the fan of reggae##1
 9. the ranch-style house is between the person driving the scooter and the person who's birthday is in december##2
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
12. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of jazz is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
